{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In <i>WAG</i>, you are a survivor in an underground bunker overrun by zombies. Your objective is simple: rescue the civilians and guide them safely back to the exit. However, the path is full of challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2829430/extras/steam_store_zombies.gif?t=1729023609\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Action in Closed Environments</strong>: The entire action takes place inside a bunker, with narrow corridors and dark areas that test your awareness and reaction.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Energy Issues</strong>: Power outages and system failures happen frequently, leaving you vulnerable at critical moments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Civilian Rescue</strong>: Navigate the bunker and save the remaining civilians. The return to the exit is always a race against time and danger.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Zombie Combat</strong>: Be ready to face zombies that can appear at any moment and from any direction.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>WAG</i> offers a straightforward experience, focused on the essentials: explore the bunker, survive, and complete your objectives to reach the exit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2829430/extras/steam_store_exit.gif?t=1729023609\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2829430/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1729023609","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2829430/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1729023609","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2829430/056697fcf0626431090641e4714b96274e25af04/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1729023609"